headline: Stock Market Today: Trading Resumes, Dow Rises; Google Leads While Nvidia, Tesla Eye Key Levels (Live Coverage)
summary: Futures for the Dow Jones Industrial Average and other major indexes rose slightly on Black Friday after an long overnight outage. Google-parent Alphabet continued to lead the market, while Nvidia, Tesla, Robinhood Markets and GE Vernova worked to reclaim key support on the stock market today.
